We are using sysid this year to tune our drivetrain. However sysid does not make our robot actually move. It deploys to the robot successfully and says nt connected. The lights on our spark max are solid cyan when we enable the sysid software in autonomous. Sysid also gives us the encoder and gyro readings when we disable autonomous. I cannot seem to find the problem. I do not have screenshots of it right now but will be able to attach some in an hour or so.

We had the same error but we somehow solved the problem. Here is the method:
1-Load the config file
2-Deploy
3-Set units per rotation
4-Enable auto

If you do something other than the things above it might not work. You need to open the sysid program only once per run. (If something goes wrong close the program then restart the proces). This method works for us. I hope it helps.
